  "remarks": "After the illegal annexation of Crimea, Russian National Commercial Bank (RNCB) became fully owned by the so-called “Republic of Crimea”. In January 2016, it became a property of the Federal Agency for State Property Management, also known as Rosimushchestvo (Федеральное агентство по управлению государственным имуществом (Росимущество)).",
